title: Joanne Fluke-Peach Cobbler Murder
description:
Joanne Fluke	 	 FICTION / Mystery & Detective 

In Peach Cobbler Murder, Fluke returns to the charming town of Lake Eden, Minnesota only to find her beloved heroine embroiled in her stickiest situation yet.
Georgia transplants Shawna Lee and Vanessa have opened a bakery to rival Hannahs own, but when one of the Southern belles is murdered, Hannah must find the killer before she herself becomes a suspect.
